{"tid":1718160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普稱距離與中國簽署首階段協議又近一步","createTime":"2019-11-13T19:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T20:20:36.000Z","uid":125193,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca74948cd18ae925aead552b30f6e6de1be1494","tid":1718160,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:09:03.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普表示，距離與中國簽署首階段貿易協議又近一步，應會在近期簽署，但強調只會接受對美方有利的協議。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n他在紐約演講時又警告，若談判破裂會考慮12月大幅上調對中國貨品的關稅。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>特朗普指，中國已成為全球第二經濟大國，但在世貿組織仍作為發展中國家享受優待措施，強調沒有哪個國家比中國騙取的好處更多。</strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，特朗普又自誇美國經濟實現大大超過預期的增長，並批評聯儲局減息幅度不足，令美國與其他國家競爭，處於不利狀態。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491931-20191113.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491931-20191113.htm&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=70c9c4bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491931-20191113.htm&h=f0120922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491931-20191113.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2e6092d79f998d2289cb36303a7145b5542b780d","tid":1718160,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:10:26.000Z","msg":"禮拜四救下市，大驚小怪"},{"pid":"9f7d4577f1d45102b3d1116445a4eb29cabea83f","tid":1718160,"uid":227271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:12:22.000Z","msg":"唔好十二月啦，依家啦，頂唔順啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b74c29253f4332831b71596a4b2ca9c493cc8a","tid":1718160,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h0xXNNW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh0xXNNW.jpg&h=c4b816da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38ba6f482ebfadb86c00a867cde7f